<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<CONTENT id="_3793145_1"><TITLE value="Session 5"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;h5&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884698_1" alt="" width="564" height="189" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5&gt;News&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/content/ia/article/2024/ato-cops-4-7m-cyber-attacks-every-month.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM20742" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;ATO cops 4.7m cyber attacks every month | Information Age | ACS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.abc.net.au/news/2025-02-19/genea-ivf-investigating-cyber-incident/104954470" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://www.abc.net.au/news/2025-02-19/genea-ivf-investigating-cyber-incident/104954470&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Australian Cyber Security Strategy (2023-2030) ACTION PLAN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;reflects the current Australian Government's ambitions to better secure the country's cyber security future. This is a political document subject to all those limits of such documents.&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-52744692_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;2023-cyber-security-strategy-action-plan.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The Australian government &lt;strong&gt;Privacy Act 1988&lt;/strong&gt; "overhaul"&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2024/doxxing-criminalised-as-privacy-act-overhaul-begins.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Doxxing criminalised as Privacy Act overhaul begins | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;While we are on the topic&lt;strong&gt; please read &lt;/strong&gt;the&lt;strong&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.oaic.gov.au/privacy/australian-privacy-principles/australian-privacy-principles-quick-reference" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Australian Privacy Principles quick reference | OAIC&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884699_1" alt="" width="382" height="215" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Session Topic:&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;During the session we investigate the various&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt; methods and techiques employed to protect personal data and privacy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Identity and Access Management (IAM, ponounced&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt; I am&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Protection from cyber threats&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The known Cyber attacks identified and characterised&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;How they work, what vulnerabilities are exploited.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul style="list-style-type: disc;"&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Identity and Access Management&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;Identity and access management (IAM)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; is the cybersecurity discipline that deals with how users access digital resources and what they can do with those resources. &lt;br&gt;IAM systems keep hackers out while ensuring that each individual user has the exact permissions they need to do their jobs and not more than that.&lt;br&gt;This is most relevant to the "C", &lt;strong&gt;Confidentiality&lt;/strong&gt; and to a lesser extent the "I", &lt;strong&gt;Integrity&lt;/strong&gt; of the cyber security principles &lt;strong&gt;CIA &lt;/strong&gt;triad.&lt;br&gt;Applying &lt;strong&gt;Authetication, Authorization and Accounting&lt;/strong&gt; (AAA) methods are an important part of IAM.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-65716465_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials - Access Control.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XQ8GDSUUvPY" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Access Control Models (Professor Messer, youtube.com)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hZ2voph67v8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Access Control Technologies (Professor Messer, youtube.com)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Note: These access control models are also discussed in the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security Fundamentals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; Session 12.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;slot&gt;&lt;div id="table-of-contents-dd742f2c6b"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div id="body-4bf72e5543"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div id="container-4356937a8f"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;dds-content-block-segmented content-section-body="" no-image="" data-autoid="dds--content-block-segmented"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;slot name="copy"&gt;&lt;dds-content-block-copy size="md" slot="copy" data-autoid="dds--content-block__copy"&gt;&lt;slot&gt;&lt;dds-content-block-paragraph data-autoid="dds--content-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;slot&gt;&lt;div data-dynamic-inner-content="description" id="rich-text-7c6e0df5ed"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/slot&gt;&lt;/dds-content-block-paragraph&gt;&lt;/slot&gt;&lt;/dds-content-block-copy&gt;&lt;/slot&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/dds-content-block-segmented&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/slot&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Portfolio Tasks:&lt;br&gt;AT1 Part-Three Essentials&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884700_1" alt="" width="279" height="360" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Setup Windows client machine&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Configure networking elements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Capture packets with Wireshark using Telnet and SSH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Out of Session Activity:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Check assessments tab.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Complete outstanding work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
